asap.motionunit

Class TimedMotionUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • asap.realizer.planunit.TimedAbstractPlanUnit
      • asap.motionunit.TimedMotionUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    asap.realizer.planunit.TimedPlanUnit

    public class TimedMotionUnit
extends asap.realizer.planunit.TimedAbstractPlanUnit
    A timedmotionunit is an abstract plan unit that delegates playback of motion to a motion unit. It takes care of translating the 'real' time into time values between 0 and 1 used in this motion unit.
    Author:
    hvanwelbergen
